<main class="mt-5">
  <p id="notice"></p>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p style="font-size:50px;">VISITORS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-2"></div>
        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="3"></li>
          </ol>
          <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/static/AMEMAN51019_TP_V4.JPG" alt="First slide">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/static/shikun81421092_TP_V4-2.JPG" alt="Second slide">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/static/011KZ21329_TP_V4.JPG" alt="Third slide">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
              <img class="d-block w-100" src="/static/img_9323.JPG" alt="Third slide">
              <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4"></div>
        <div class="form-row text-center">
          <div class="col-12">
          <% if user_signed_in? %>
        　<label for="post" class="col-mt-2"></label>
        　　<%= link_to " 投稿一覧へ【LIST UP】", posts_path, class: "btn btn-primary shadow fas fa-list-ul" %>
        　<label for="new" class="col-mt-2"></label>
        　　<%= link_to " 新規投稿【NEW】", new_post_path, class: "btn btn-success shadow fas fa-plus" %>
        　<label for="plan" class="col-mt-2"></label>
        　　<%= link_to " 旅行計画【PLAN】", new_plan_path, class: "btn btn-dark shadow fas fa-plus" %>
        　<% else %>
        　<label for="registration" class="col-mt-2"></label>
            <%= link_to " 新規登録", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary shadow btn-lg fas fa-user-plus" %>
          <label for="session" class="col-mt-2"></label>
            <%= link_to " ログイン", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-primary shadow btn-lg fas fa-sign-in-alt" %>
        　<% end %>
        </div>
        <div class="p-3"></div>
        <div class="col-12">
        <div class="p-2"></div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p>本アプリは一人旅を計画するための管理アプリです</p>
          <p>旅先で実際に泊まった宿を投稿・公開したり、</p>
          <p>一人旅行に向けた旅行計画を立てることができます</p>
          <p>投稿一覧の閲覧は可能ですが、投稿や詳細の閲覧などができない為</p>
          <p>本アプリを使用する際は、新規登録かログインが必要になります</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>